        {
            "title": "中國央行貨幣政策例會表述對比:維持適度寬鬆基調 新增「跨周期」調節",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國人民銀行周三發布貨幣政策委員會第四季度例會公告，在維持「適度寬鬆」基調的同時，釋放著眼長遠的信號。央行新增了「跨周期」調節的表述，強調要增強宏觀政策的「前瞻性針對性協同性」，提出要「優化供給，做優增量、盤活存量」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於國內經濟，央行的措辭從「國內需求不足」變為「供強需弱矛盾突出」，不再點名「物價低位運行」，但在政策目標方面明確提出要「促進物價合理回升」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣政策方面，央行稱下一階段要「發揮增量政策和存量政策集成效應，綜合運用多種工具」，並新增了把握好政策實施「時機」的表述。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6123ae11-f93e-38c3-916f-16aaf8259868-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於信貸及融資，央行本季度刪去了「引導金融機構加大貨幣信貸投放力度」的說法，稱要促進社會綜合融資成本「低位運行」，而非上一季度主張的「推動」其「下降」，並刪除了「防範資金空轉」的表述。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，央行對債市和人民幣的表述整體延續上一季度的基調，同時未再單列房地產相關內容。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E8%B2%A8%E5%B9%A3%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E4%BE%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%A1%A8%E8%BF%B0%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94-%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E9%81%A9%E5%BA%A6%E5%AF%AC%E9%AC%86%E5%9F%BA%E8%AA%BF-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-%E8%B7%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F-%E8%AA%BF%E7%AF%80-162051800.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-25 01:45:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "在清淡的假日交易中 英國股市下跌 法國股市基本持平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 英國股市小幅走低，法國股市基本持平，交易清淡，而歐洲多數主要股市因聖誕假期休市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國CAC 40指數基本持平，英國富時100指數下跌0.2%。兩個市場均僅進行半日交易，成交量低於平均水平。德國、義大利、丹麥、瑞士和芬蘭股市全天休市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，法國製藥巨頭賽諾菲股價下跌，此前該公司宣布美國食品藥品監督管理局對其多發性硬化癥實驗性藥物發出完整答復函。該法國藥企還同意以約22億美元收購Dynavax Technologies。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-88520373-8b68-3a5d-a37a-8baa7cf44269-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BP公司股價收跌0.4%，此前該公司同意將其嘉實多業務中的多數股份出售給美國投資公司Stonepeak Partners，交易對業務估值（含債務）達101億美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u_UvK5RfldGAJiPD14U2Uw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a04a0a5f2d550344093e4a7f7af16166\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲斯托克600指數周二再創紀錄新高，在全球經濟成長前景持續樂觀及借貸成本走低的推動下，有望實現連續第三年上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">瑞訊銀行高級分析師Ipek Ozkardeskaya表示，股市在年底最後幾天仍可能繼續上漲。「但之後呢？現實可能令人失望。科技市場部分板塊可能存在泡沫，明年財報季的焦點將不再是亮眼的數字，而是實際收入的來源。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題UK Stocks Dip, French Shares Subdued in Thin Holiday Trading</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sagarika Jaisinghani.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%85%E6%B7%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%81%87%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E4%B8%AD-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%8C%81%E5%B9%B3-133932295.html",
